```plantuml
@startuml leekoko_Java-Web

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend\n(Java Servlets/Spring Boot)" as BE
participant "Dubbo RPC" as Dubbo
participant "Dubbo Registry" as Registry
participant "Data Storage\n(Redis, MySQL)" as DB

User -> FE: Initiates Request
FE -> BE: Sends HTTP Request
BE -> Registry: Service Discovery
Registry -> BE: Service Details
BE -> Dubbo: Invoke Remote Service
Dubbo -> BE: Remote Service Executed
BE -> DB: Query/Update Database
DB -> BE: Return Data
BE -> FE: Send HTTP Response
FE -> User: Display Result

@enduml
```